name: 2010 - Enivornmental, I'm not a Calendar, Calendar
description: "As seen in Creative Review". World Wildlife Fund - "In the last 30 years we have already consumed a third of the world's natural resources." To show our commitment to environment, I bring you "I'm not a Calendar, Calendar". All the pages of the calendar are 100% recyclable but not only that each month can be reused - as they unwrap to a larger sized print which can reused as gift-wrapping or as a poster. Commissioned by and Concept by: Qube Studios Prints: 12 designs are taken from my portfolio of self-initiated works and follows the theme of the Cube. Paper: 9lives 55 Silk using soy-based inks. Shipping: to UK only
